A vintage-style illustration of a silver-haired person sitting contentedly at a wooden desk in a warm, sunlit home office, their face illuminated by the soft glow of an old CRT monitor displaying a penguin mascot. Surrounding them are scattered CD cases and worn computer manuals, a steaming cup of tea nearby. Through a window behind them, a peaceful garden is visible. The scene has the warm, nostalgic color palette of 1970s magazine illustrations with slightly desaturated oranges, browns, and creams. The atmosphere conveys quiet curiosity and the joy of learning something new, with dust motes floating in afternoon light beams streaming through venetian blinds.
